import { Tab, Tabs, TabList, TabPanel } from 'react-tabs'; import 'react-tabs/style/react-tabs.css'; import Headings from './Headings'; export default ({ resumedata }) => { console.log(resumedata, 'resumedata'); const mainContent = resumedata?.maincontent || []; return ( <>
education professional Skills experience interview {mainContent.map((section, sectionIndex) => (
{section.year}

{section.heading}

{section.resumeinfo.length > 0 ? ( section.resumeinfo.map((item, index) => (

{item.title}

{item.university}
{item.rating}

{item.content}

)) ) : (

No resume information available.

)}
))}
); };
